{
  "stem": "182.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 65.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Then, at lunch time, they brought some kind of vegetables cooked together with some barley or something.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But it was cooked I don't know what time, and it was in big containers, like milk containers.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And then you opened it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was kind of bubbling, like it's getting fermented.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "It's-- it's-- it was awful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "It was grey and smelly, and-- and the worst part was that each 10 people, they had one bowl.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And they put this gruel in this bowl, and you had to pass it around.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And everybody-- there was no spoons.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Everybody slobbered into it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "I could never eat it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "They told me I'm going to die, but I just couldn't eat it.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And in the evening, then, after that, we went out again in the a-- eve-- about four o'clock, and we have to stand in rows again, and we were counted.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And when we came back, then everybody got a little piece of bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And one day it was a little marmalade, one day it was a slice like liverwurst, one day it was a little patch of margarine.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And this was what we lived on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I-- I never ate.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Not the-- the breakfast.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Sometimes for breakfast they had like [?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "Farina. ?] But it-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "They maybe sweetened it with saccharin or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "It was terribly sweet and-- and bad.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "So this bread and this little something kept us going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Now, this-- from this barrack, they took us over to a place that was called a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "This housed about 32,000 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "It was a long, long area, barracks on both sides.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "As you came in, the Germans had their-- a little house for themselves.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And on the two sides were the kitchens, two kitchens.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And then the barracks went like this.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
